{"tid":657211,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"華爾街Downtown 住宅100萬美元上車　","createTime":"2018-05-08T01:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T07:38:47.000Z","uid":2644,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ed89e734bfad080c2f149e15ebef399d206f9ee4","tid":657211,"uid":2644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T01:59:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">華爾街住宅百萬美元入場</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f9/1_Wall_Street_panoramic.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Ff%2Ff9%2F1_Wall_Street_panoramic.jpg&h=5766e036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n位於美國紐約曼哈頓下城區的華爾街，一直是國際金融市場焦點。樓齡約87年的One Wall Street將改建為住宅項目，提供566伙，本月11日至13日於本港進行展銷，入場費料不足100萬美元（約780萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\nOne Wall Street樓高50層，位於曼哈頓下城區華爾街及百老滙大道交界，過去曾先後稱為歐文信託公司大廈（Irving Trust Company Building）和紐約梅隆銀行大廈（BNY Mellon Building），現正進行重新設計，擬提供566個住宅單位，<strong><ins>標準戶實用面積約688至3000方呎，開放式至4房間隔</ins></strong>，另設頂層複式連天台戶，實用面積逾12000方呎，預計2020年落成。<br />\n<br />\n美國物業代理CORE創辦人及行政總裁Shaun Osher指出，市場對曼哈頓下城區住宅的需求殷切，<strong><ins>現時區內平均呎價約2000美元（約15600港元）</ins></strong>，價格走勢表現平穩。<br />\n<br />\n仲量聯行國際住宅部主管黃嘉欣認為，華爾街近年愈來愈多創意工業及初創企業進駐，對住宅有強大需求，吸引發展商在該區發展住宅，形成全新的生活圈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.thecityreview.com/downtown/financial/wall1z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thecityreview.com%2Fdowntown%2Ffinancial%2Fwall1z.jpg&h=a20ad159&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"748804db83255dd9f882636583b3c2896036dfd0","tid":657211,"uid":2644,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T02:01:29.000Z","msg":"Manhattan downtown平均呎價仲平過屯門山旮旯地區新盤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e49c6af07258095dfb8d2bbbeb8d8056f6b188","tid":657211,"uid":53660,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T02:08:21.000Z","msg":"御半山屈機好多"},{"pid":"081f05944bb8ba204086a22269ad084e527195fd","tid":657211,"uid":48277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T02:09:51.000Z","msg":"海之戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82307a0bd33da84a2b2d06987665abb5822f1f70","tid":657211,"uid":10101,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T02:14:12.000Z","msg":"華爾街咪同鴨寮街差唔多水平<br />\n唔值咁貴"},{"pid":"c2f3a69e8941fea0d839d4da9109ff938e0efc2d","tid":657211,"uid":1327,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"748804db83255dd9f882636583b3c2896036dfd0","tid":657211,"uid":2644,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T02:01:29.000Z","msg":"Manhattan downtown平均呎價仲平過屯門山旮旯地區新盤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T02:16:38.000Z","msg":"俾你住開長島 2千呎 house <br />\n連私人游泳池都可能唔駛咁貴<br />\n你會唔會搬黎住呢到 ? <br />\n<br />\n鬼佬住開 house , 尤求結左婚<br />\ncondo 同 apartment 跟本唔會考慮<br />\n要炒樓都唔會炒 apartment <br />\n<br />\n講真 香港地有錢買樓不如移民<br />\n唔好望住香港呢d 垃圾地方<br />\n羅8百萬就有2/3 千呎 , 幾個廁所<br />\n十尻幾間房 , 仲有私人泳池 , 駛撚同人爭同人逼<br />\n你係香港搵幾錢先有私人泳池？<br />\n仲未計下一代教育 就算6歲先要番學<br />\n10歲英文就好過廿歲香港人<br />\n未計福利之類<br />\n<br />\n你話你呢代可能融入唔到<br />\n起馬你仔女 abc 一定冇問題<br />\n仲會多謝爸爸移民移得好 , 有真正的自由<br />\n<br />\n可必生個仔出黎仲要佢望住5百呎籠屋係到打飛機"},{"pid":"efc9275d14196dbda02f400d96243afe648cf522","tid":657211,"uid":3177,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T02:17:25.000Z","msg":"嗱！ 人地就可以大大隻字 寫住 華爾街1號啦 <br />\n香港啲私樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ef74dcf93afbdbf63f1